                          [PLANNING DEVELOPMENT ROADMAP]
                                       |
         +-----------------------------+-----------------------------+
         |                             |                             |
         v                             v                             v
  [STAGE 1: Rule-Based Systems]         [STAGE 2: Adaptive Planning]  [STAGE 3: Decentralized Mesh]
   Manual constraint solvers.           Self-improving templates.     Distributed multi-device runs.
   Hardcoded policy-guard gates.        Auto-recalibration parameters.Sovereign economic execution.

